Maelle Heath has been an elementary music teacher for 30+ years.  She has a Bachelor’s degree in Music Education and a Master of Science degree in Elementary Education with a Gifted and Talented Endorsement, both from Indiana University.  Her classroom has long included the use of technology to engage students and increase musical understanding.  Intergalactic Music Missions is a series of interactive recorder and musical concept textbooks by Mrs. Heath.
